description:
The sheet music for my arrangement of Nara on the piano. It's not exactly right, but it's the best I could do with the time I had - This is also my first arrangement to paper, but hopefully it's still readable. 
Here is the video of me playing it on youtube - there is also a spoken tutorial for it if you check my other videos.
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xqYk0Va7HkA
title: Nara - E.S. Posthumus - Piano
